\c 14
\s Asa mambo waJudha
\p
\v 1 Zvino Abhija akarara namadzibaba ake, akavigwa muguta raDhavhidhi; Asa mwanakomana wake akamutevera paushe, pamazuva ake nyika yakange ino rugare makore ane gumi.
\v 2 Asa akaita zvakanaka nezvakarurama pamberi paJehovha Mwari wake.
\v 3 Nokuti akabvisa aritari dzoutorwa, namatunhu akakwirira, akaputsa shongwe, nokutemawo matanda okunamata nawo;
\v 4 akaraira vaJudha kuti vatsvake Jehovha Mwari wamadzibaba avo, nokuchengeta murau nomurayiro.
\v 5 Akabvisawo pamaguta ose avaJudha matunhu akakwirira nezvimwari zvezuva; ushe hukava norugare iye ari mambo.
\v 6 Akavaka maguta akakombwa paJudha; nokuti nyika yakange ino rugare, akange asina kurwa pamakore iwayo; nokuti Jehovha akange amuzorodza.
\v 7 Nokuti akati kuvaJudha: Ngativake maguta iwayo, tiapoteredze namasvingo, neshongwe, namasuwo, namazariro; nyika ichiri pamberi pedu, nokuti takatsvaka Jehovha Mwari wedu; takamutsvaka, akatizorodza pamativi ose. Ipapo vakavaka, vakagara zvakanaka.
\v 8 Asa akange ane hondo yavaJudha, vane zviuru zvina mazana matatu, vakange vakashonga nhovo huru namapfumo; neyavaBhenjamini vane zviuru zvina mazana maviri namakumi masere, vakange vakashonga nhovo vaifura nouta; ava vese vaiva varume vane simba noumhare.
\p
\v 9 Zvino Zera multiopia akauya kuzorwa navo nehondo yavanhu vane zviuru zvezviuru, nengoro dzina mazana matatu; akasvika Maresha.
\p
\v 10 Ipapo Asa akabuda kuzorwa naye, vakagadzira kuzorwa pamupata weZefata paMaresha.
\v 11 Asa akachema kuna Jehovha Mwari wake, akati, Jehovha hakuna angabatsira asine simba kurwa nounesimba, asi imwi moga; tibatsirei Jehovha Mwari wedu; nokuti tinovimba nemi, tasvika kuzorwa navazhinji ava nezita renyu. imwi Jehovha, ndimi Mwari wedu; munhu ngaarege kukukundai imi.
\p
\v 12 Ipapo Jehovha akaparadza vaKushi pamberi paAsa, napamberi pavaJudha, vaKushi vakatiza.
\v 13 Asa navanhu vaakange anavo vakavateverera kusvikira paGerari; vaKushi vakaurawa vazhinji, vakakoniwa kumutsiridzika; nokuti vakaparadzwa pamberi paJehovha napamberi pehondo yake vaJudha vakaenda nezvizhinji kwazvo zvavakapamba.
\v 14 Vakaparadza maguta ose akapoteredza Gerari; nokuti vakavhunduswa naJehovha; vakapamba maguta ose, nokuti kwakange kune zvingapambiwa zvizhinji maari.
\v 15 Vakaparadzawo matende ezvipfuwo, vakatapa makwai mazhinji nemakamera, ndokudzokera Jerusarema.
